Recruiting class national rankings have risen significantly since Endelman began his tenure as head coach of Columbia men’s tennis

The average ranking before Edelman became head coach, from 2006 to 2019, was 14.625. Since Endelman’s first season as coach in 2019-20, the average ranking has risen to 5.0.
